2563
01:39:07,750 --> 01:39:13,580
[Ink out]

2564
01:39:10,560 --> 01:39:12,960
Commander R: Ink out.

2565
01:39:14,060 --> 01:39:16,390
[Ink out]

2566
01:39:14,670 --> 01:39:15,960
Commander R: Ink out.

2567
01:39:17,060 --> 01:39:19,920
[Ink out]

2568
01:39:17,060 --> 01:39:19,050
