2579
01:40:10,380 --> 01:40:13,240
Commander R: Daou out.

2580
01:40:10,630 --> 01:40:13,910
[Daou out]

2581
01:40:15,260 --> 01:40:17,110
Phuak: Jeff, Jeff.

2582
01:40:17,080 --> 01:40:20,360
