-Daou: I'm fine, bro.
-Phuak: Daou, are you okay?

2597
01:41:15,770 --> 01:41:16,490
Daou: Dead.

2598
01:41:15,890 --> 01:41:18,430
[(Phuak) is dead]

2599
01:41:16,540 --> 01:41:17,350
Phuak: Daou.

2600
01:41:18,550 --> 01:41:20,350
-Daou: Dead.
-Phuak: Daou.

2601
01:41:18,700 --> 01:41:20,890
[(Phuak) is dead]

2602
