01:41:35,390 --> 01:41:37,600
Phuak: Daou, you little brat.

2609
01:41:37,650 --> 01:41:39,440
Daou: Shh, keep it down.

2610
01:41:41,800 --> 01:41:42,580
Daou: Right now

2611
01:41:42,580 --> 01:41:44,710
Daou: I need to get out of here fast,
