2612
01:41:44,710 --> 01:41:46,770
Daou: They'll wonder
how Phuak died.

2613
01:41:47,020 --> 01:41:49,280
Daou: I'm going to finish this game, bro.

2614
01:41:49,660 --> 01:41:51,310
Daou: I'm off. Bye.

2615
01:41:51,540 --> 01:41:54,330
[Run before anyone notices]

2616
01:41:54,620 --> 01:41:57,250
[Phuak out]

2617
