Phuak: Who took you out?

2629
01:42:20,860 --> 01:42:21,730
Ink: Tay.

2630
01:42:21,990 --> 01:42:23,900
Ink: He betrayed me.

2631
01:42:24,680 --> 01:42:27,880
[In shock, refusing to accept reality]

2632
01:42:25,570 --> 01:42:26,900
Phuak: That Daou…

2633
01:42:27,920 --> 01:42:29,120
Phuak: such a bad guy.

2634
01:42:29,930 --> 01:42:33,180
[Daou, I'll remember this]

2635
01:42:33,720 --> 01:42:35,910
[Jeff is searching for something]

2636
