2668
01:44:51,900 --> 01:44:53,960
Daou: We need to team up, the three of us.

2669
01:44:53,960 --> 01:44:55,360
Daou: Oat is downstairs.

2670
01:44:57,050 --> 01:44:58,820
Daou: Pramote Pathan.

2671
