Jeff: There aren't
many people left now, bro.

2675
01:45:10,840 --> 01:45:11,650
Oat: Okay.

2676
01:45:11,830 --> 01:45:13,890
Oat: We can settle it here if you want.

2677
01:45:14,580 --> 01:45:16,620
Jeff: If I fire, it's deadly.

2678
01:45:16,640 --> 01:45:18,300
Jeff: One shot and you're out.

2679
01:45:20,040 --> 01:45:23,640
[Oat sticks tightly to the wall.
Jeff can't attack him at all]

2680
01:45:25,790 --> 01:45:27,650
Daou: I'm going to hold your arm, bro.

2681
01:45:27,650 --> 01:45:28,580
Daou: I'm outnumbered here, bro.

2682
01:45:28,580 --> 01:45:30,180
Oat: No, no.

2683
01:45:36,020 --> 01:45:37,280
Jeff: Oat.

2684
01:45:37,400 --> 01:45:38,440
Oat: No, no.

2685
01:45:38,550 --> 01:45:39,250
Jeff: Oat.

2686
01:45:39,370 --> 01:45:40,650
Daou: He's so strong at pulling people.

2687
01:45:40,650 --> 01:45:41,390
Jeff: Oat.

2688
01:45:41,390 --> 01:45:44,630
Daou: That pulling force is insane,
