Pretend you can't see me]

2698
01:46:14,880 --> 01:46:17,800
Oat: Buzz, stealth, buzz.

2699
01:46:18,130 --> 01:46:19,670
Jeff: Huh? Where did Oat go?

2700
01:46:19,700 --> 01:46:22,290
[Run]

2701
01:46:22,170 --> 01:46:24,320
Jeff: Huh? Where did he go? Oat!

2702
01:46:26,710 --> 01:46:27,840
Daou: Where'd he go?

2703
01:46:35,700 --> 01:46:40,140
[Time 00:43:91]

2704
01:46:37,360 --> 01:46:40,140
[Only 43 seconds left!]

2705
01:46:40,210 --> 01:46:41,310
Jeff: Run after him!

2706
01:46:41,310 --> 01:46:43,240
Daou: Shall we chase him?
Chase him—he's weak right now.

2707
01:46:43,240 --> 01:46:45,170
-Tay: Follow the footprints.
-Jeff: He's still on cooldown.

2708
01:46:45,170 --> 01:46:48,170
Tay: Cooldown…
Is this his first time using the skill?

2709
01:46:50,430 --> 01:46:51,490
Oat: My friends.

2710
01:46:52,340 --> 01:46:54,490
Oat: Hey, 3 against 1?

2711
01:46:55,650 --> 01:46:56,910
Oat: That works for me.

2712
01:47:09,060 --> 01:47:14,430
[The three power players
gather one after another]

2713
01:47:09,580 --> 01:47:10,800
-Oat: I've got it.
-Daou: No, you haven't.

2714
01:47:10,800 --> 01:47:11,720
-Oat: I've got it.
-Daou: No, you haven't.

2715
01:47:11,720 --> 01:47:12,690
Oat: I've got it.

2716
01:47:12,720 --> 01:47:14,590
Daou: I can't rip it off.

2717
01:47:16,260 --> 01:47:18,180
Oat: Buzz, stealth.

2718
01:47:18,560 --> 01:47:20,840
[Even with only the last 10 seconds left,
