2742
01:48:20,410 --> 01:48:21,140
Oat: Come on.

2743
01:48:21,160 --> 01:48:22,010
Daou: Jeff!

2744
01:48:22,130 --> 01:48:25,330
-Tay: Even 3 people can't rip it off!
-Daou: Tay, hold him!

2745
01:48:30,860 --> 01:48:32,260
Tay: Jeff, hang in there!

2746
01:48:38,050 --> 01:48:40,260
[Get ready for a final showdown]

2747
01:48:53,070 --> 01:48:54,600
Jeff: He got hit! He got hit!

2748
01:48:55,460 --> 01:48:57,170
Daou: It's off!

2749
01:48:58,860 --> 01:49:01,120
Commander R: Oat out.

2750
01:49:01,310 --> 01:49:03,940
Commander R: Oat out.

2751
01:49:04,850 --> 01:49:09,540
[The final battle of
the last 3 officially begins]

2752
01:49:12,310 --> 01:49:13,230
Daou: Lie down.

2753
